#How call this package: 
```{r}
install_github('AmberlyDziesinski/ds')
library(ds)

data("vote_gov_states")
data("vote_pres_national")
data("vote_pres_primaries")
data("vote_pres_states")
data("vote_sen_states")
data("hsls")

?vote_gov_states
?vote_pres_national
?vote_pres_primaries
?vote_pres_states
?vote_sen_states
?hsls
```
